CNC is tantamount with INTEGRITY, INNOVATION and EXCELLENCE.

EDUCATION IS THE MOST POWERFULL WEAPON WHICH YOU CAN USE TO CHANGE THE WORLD.

CNC Network creates IT professionals by training youth and students in multiple segments of Information Technology. Our training aims at understanding, teaching & applying features and functionality of various software's applicable in Designing, Website Design & Development, Accounting & Taxation, Programming, Hardware & Networking etc.

 

We have experienced work lovers focused on quality. 

Diploma in Computer Applications

English & Hindi Typing, MS Office, Internet

Level Up Web Technologies

Web Desinging, Angular Js, Node Js, React Js, and More.

Course on Computer Concepts

Basic, OS, Office, Internet, Social Networking, Tools, Cyber Security

RSC-IT

Fundamental, Windows, MS Office, Internet, Hardwares, Cyber Security

Advance Basics

English & Hindi Typing, MS Office, Internet

Advance Excel

Basic, Formulas, Functions, Conditional Formatting, Sort & Filter, Pivot Table, Chart, VBA Macros

Diploma in Financial Accounting

Advance Excel, Tally Accounting, Inventory, Taxation, Advance Tally

Diploma in Programming

C, C++, Python, Core Java, Advance JAVA

Contact now !

Be a part a great Revolution

ABOUT

CNC Infotech Skill Development Private Limited is a foundation standing strong since 22 years in the business, focusing into software development and IT educational enterprise that firmly believes in empowering young minds with skills and enlightening them with knowledge to be the future leaders. CNC is tantamount with INTEGRITY, INNOVATION and EXCELLENCE
